description: Don't you hate when you get a parking ticket? Chyna does and she is determined to contest it, she goes to the address given to her by the officer and finds herself in the wrong place, at the wrong time. She is grabbed from behind and slapped, she struggles and tries to scream but the grip is too tight, feet scuffle, muffled cries are heard and a light bulb is smashed...all goes dark. She is powerless and has no idea what will happen next.
title: ABDUCTION FANTASY
